{"tid":1421514,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"其實你仲記唔記得五大訴求?","createTime":"2019-08-06T08:17:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T08:20:06.000Z","uid":140354,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"aeb3d60b7c39f5b6cc4dad7d8edfeb2efcb14b9d","tid":1421514,"uid":140354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:17:02.000Z","msg":"而家好似好少人提起「五大訴求」<br />\n重中之重, 係基本法講明嘅<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">雙普選</span></strong>, 呢個係五大訴求嘅根本<br />\n<br />\n「光復香港, 時代革命」可以講, 但係冇理由講得多過五大訴求<br />\n就好似頭先民間記者會咁講, 個個人對「光復香港, 時代革命」都可以有自己解釋<br />\n表達嘅意思, 相對上真係比較空泛<br />\n唔好因為有人話唔好講, 就鬥氣去講<br />\n講返多D五大訴求, 尤其係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">雙普選</span></strong>, 好唔好? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n明明一開始大家就係向住呢個目標走出嚟<br />\n打狗緊要, 打黑緊要, 但係記唔記得最終目標係咩, 五大訴求呀 <br />\n還我<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">真雙普選</span></strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac36db34622709bb6b54c8846a4e12a796c272b7","tid":1421514,"uid":282624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:17:41.000Z","msg":"我要自由<br />\n我要民主<br />\n我要真普選"},{"pid":"66d287ed0fa77c1ed8d43c77d2565b6fc8f2a0fa","tid":1421514,"uid":101392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:19:51.000Z","msg":"樓主講左我想講嘅嘢 我都差D想開post<br />\n林鄭話佢回應曬五大訴求<br />\n雙普選連回應都無回應過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連推搪、解釋都懶"},{"pid":"069fa6658c0ca8bb41ed711d7810d040ddffee18","tid":1421514,"uid":140354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:20:06.000Z","msg":"咁都負評我, 我有咩講錯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}